### this final project is basically anaylsis the relationship between covid 19 vaccinations and new cases and deathes. 


### notebook directory
The report is loacte at notebook/Fan-Modified.html, which generated by Fan-Modified.ipynb in same directory. 

Please look the HTML file for final project because it contains more detailed information including but not limited in Interactive Visulization and Data Correlation computation. 


The Basic step of our project is requests data from online and store the data in local as csv, then using data munging to extract the finalized dataset and store the data using sql. Then performing visualiaztion to analysis the problem we want to find.
